data.description: Discover the allure of this meticulously maintained 3 bedroom/2 bath home in Ocala's premier 55+ community, Marion Landing. Brimming with charm, the residence welcomes you with natural light, and a formal living and dining space. The well-equipped kitchen features ample cabinets, Stainless Steel appliances, and a windowed breakfast nook. Enjoy leisurely moments in the enclosed lanai. Recent upgrades include a New AC in 2022, Roof in 2017, Windows in 2011 and 2014, and a New Storm door in 2022. With low HOA fees covering Water, Sewer, and Trash, this home offers both comfort and convenience. The community amenities, including a Clubhouse, Bowling Alley, Solar Heated Swimming Pool, Tennis/Pickleball Courts, and more, enhance the vibrant lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to call this your home – schedule your appointment today!
